Author: Xen
Content: ```NL!tag <name>NLNLAllows you to tag text for later retrieval.NLNLIf a subcommand is not called_ then this will search the tag databaseNLfor the tag requested.NLNLCommands:NL  alias   Creates an alias for a pre-existing tag.NL  all     Lists all server-specific tags for this server.NL  create  Creates a new tag owned by you.NL  edit    Modifies an existing tag that you own.NL  generic Creates a new generic tag owned by you.NL  info    Retrieves info about a tag.NL  list    Lists all the tags that belong to you or someone else.NL  make    Interactive makes a tag for you.NL  raw     Gets the raw content of the tag.NL  remove  Removes a tag that you own.NL  search  Searches for a tag.NL  stats   Gives stats about the tag database.NLNLType !tag command for more info on a command.NLYou can also type !tag category for more info on a category.NL```
